{"tid":635465,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】國道行駛中上演「觀音坐蓮」　網友：原來SOD都是真的","createTime":"2018-04-20T06:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T07:14:19.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1c0adffc60494f145f9cbf0830c9c348128d5e62","tid":635465,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:55:21.000Z","msg":"有民眾在臉書社團「聯結車 大貨車 大客車 拉拉隊 運輸業 照片影片資訊分享團」中張貼一段影片，畫面中一輛銀色的福特Focus轎車，疑似行經國道一號北上新竹湖口路段時，駕駛座的司機身上竟然跨坐了一個人，正在詭異的上下抖動，兩人行徑被路過駕駛全程目擊錄下，網友看了傻眼說「看魚仔在那&hellip;&hellip;咻來咻去」、「這安全氣囊不錯」、「如果開在石頭路不是更好嗎」、「人體四點式安全帶」、「原來FOCUS的避震和空間這麼好」，至於貼文的網友則表示，影片是從通訊軟體LINE經朋友分享，並非他所拍攝，但因覺得相當誇張而PO網。<br />\n國道公路警察局指出，根據《道路交通管理處罰條例》規定，駕駛人於國道上以危險方式駕車，若查證屬實可罰6000元以上、2萬4000元以下罰鍰，提醒用路人行駛公路應以安全為重，遵守交通規則，勿以危險方式駕車。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180420/1338217\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180420%2F1338217&d=NITwp9Q6aaCxncUz4%2BDeoBxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=e4abfb83\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180420%2F1338217&h=75f5b6ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180420/1338217</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180420/640_7b91d82341c40031327e802f1a8fc954.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180420%2F640_7b91d82341c40031327e802f1a8fc954.jpg&h=bd6ef12c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ff6561a4d32c460beaa6e568d198f1f18ab19c","tid":635465,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T07:14:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}